\cosh(\ln x)
\sinh(\ln x)=\frac{x-\frac{1}{x}}{2}=\frac{\frac{x^2-1}{x}}{2}=\frac{x^2-1}{2x}.
\tanh t=\frac{\sinh t}{\cosh t}
\sinh t=\frac{e^t-e^{-t}}2
\cosh t=\frac{e^t+e^{-t}}2
